Install Anaconda Navigator, community version.  
Install Spyder.
Install Chromedriver, this must be in accordance with the version of your own Chrome browser. 
e.g. if the version of your Chrome is 107 and your OS is windows, please download version 107.0.5304.62, chromedriver_win32.zip
You can find install steps in youtube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dz59GsdvUF8.
